text: Lucas Agustín Ocampo Galván (born 23 November 1997) is a Uruguayan footballer who plays as a midfielder for Liverpool Montevideo in the Uruguayan Primera División. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Liverpool F.C.
